    <item>
      <title>墨西哥向投资者保证其经济能够承受关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexico-s-finance-chief-tells-investors-it-can-withstand-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥财政部长表示，墨西哥已采取措施保护其经济免受美国关税冲击，并且各部门正在共同努力，以防货币市场的流动性受到影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexico-s-finance-chief-tells-investors-it-can-withstand-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 15:01:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管受到美国征税，倍耐力仍致力于实现减债目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/pirelli-aims-to-stick-with-debt-reduction-goal-despite-us-levies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，尽管美国即将实施的关税威胁到这家意大利轮胎制造商的北美业务，但倍耐力公司 (Pirelli &amp; C. SpA) 预计今年仍将坚持其债务削减目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/pirelli-aims-to-stick-with-debt-reduction-goal-despite-us-levies</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 14:54:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管特朗普寻求降油，OPEC+ 仍坚持供应计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/opec-sticks-to-supply-plan-even-as-trump-seeks-oil-price-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国总统唐纳德·特朗普呼吁 OPEC+ 降低原油价格，但 OPEC+ 在周一的审查会议上并未对现有的石油生产计划做出任何改变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/opec-sticks-to-supply-plan-even-as-trump-seeks-oil-price-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 14:17:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚勇敢面对市场动荡，通过出售外汇债券填补缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/romania-starts-fx-debt-sales-to-plug-deficit-amid-global-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚今年首次进入国际资本市场，在国内政局和全球投资者情绪动荡之际筹集新债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/romania-starts-fx-debt-sales-to-plug-deficit-amid-global-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 11:29:05 GMT</pubDate>
